OL,3,CMan charged after 'violent' mass brawl
OL,4,Cat transport hub
OL,6,FA man has been arrested and police
OL,7,Fhave been granted extra stop and
OL,8,Fsearch powers after a "violent" mass
OL,9,Fbrawl involving up to 30 people at a
OL,10,Ftown's transport hub.
OL,12,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP)
OL,13,Fauthorised a 24-hour Section 60 order
OL,14,Fafter reports of a significant fight
OL,15,Fat the Bolton Interchange.
OL,17,FOfficers believe several people were
OL,18,Fassaulted during the incident.
OL,19,FFollowing the disorder, police
OL,20,Fconfirmed that an 18-year-old man has
OL,21,Fbeen charged.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
