OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772615079
OL,3,CMan charged after 'violent' mass brawl
OL,4,Cat transport hub
OL,6,FAlyas Majid, of Westleigh Lane, Leigh,
OL,7,Fwas arrested and subsequently charged
OL,8,Fwith possession of a bladed article in
OL,9,Fa public place. He is due to appear at
OL,10,FWigan and Leigh Magistrates Court on 6
OL,11,FMay 2026.
OL,13,FChief Inspector John Haywood, of GMP's
OL,14,FBolton district, says extra patrols
OL,15,Fhave been deployed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
