CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772615079
OL,3,CMan charged after 'violent' mass brawl
OL,4,Cat transport hub
OL,6,F"Incidents such as this can be
OL,7,Fconcerning for the local community,
OL,8,Fbut I would like to reassure those who
OL,9,Flive and work in the area that we are
OL,10,Ffully committed to tackling violent
OL,11,Fcrime and keeping our streets safe,"
OL,12,Fhe said.
OL,14,F"The Section 60 authority has been put
OL,15,Fin place to give our officers enhanced
OL,16,Fpowers...helping us to prevent further
OL,17,Fviolence and identify those
OL,18,Fresponsible."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
