CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772615079
OL,3,CMan charged after 'violent' mass brawl
OL,4,Cat transport hub
OL,6,FThe order, which allows officers to
OL,7,Fstop and search anyone within a
OL,8,Fdefined area without needing
OL,9,F"reasonable suspicion," came into
OL,10,Feffect at 4pm on Tuesday, 3 March, and
OL,11,Fwill run until 4pm on Wednesday, 4
OL,12,FMarch.
OL,14,FThe enhanced powers cover a wide
OL,15,Fperimeter of the town centre,
OL,16,Fincluding:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
